{"categories":["survey","food-beverage","e-commerce"],"collections":"","description":"This engaging email template is designed to solicit valuable feedback from customers, particularly in the food and beverage industry. It is an excellent tool for businesses, such as pizza shops or food apps, seeking to understand their customer's experience. The template encourages users to rate their experience through a star-based survey system. This approach not only allows businesses to gain insights into their performance but also boosts customer engagement. The template is highly effective for e-commerce platforms looking to improve their services based on customer reviews. The star rating system makes it easy for customers to express their satisfaction level, making it an essential tool for businesses striving for excellence in customer service.","short_description":"Boost customer engagement with this email template designed for food and beverage businesses. Ideal for pizza shops, food apps, and e-commerce platforms, it uses a star-based survey to gain valuable customer feedback and improve services.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/IMG_20220307_130329.jpg","description":"I am a web and graphic designer deeply fascinated by UI/UX. Constantly upgrading my skills, I strive to create visually stunning and user-friendly designs and digital experiences that leave a lasting impact.","short_description":"","display_name":"Nore Potera","id":"nore-potera"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]--><!--[if !mso]><!--><link href=\"https://fonts.google